dct_title_s: Port Bou : city plan / prepared under the direction of the Chief of Engineers, U.S. Army, 1943
dct_description_sm: Map shows military and coast guard headquarters. Some streets and buildings are named. "Copied from Spanish Map, 1:20,000, Carte Topografica Militar Map Port Bou, S 30 SCME 20." "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 114983. 1943. 3-43." "Grid and projection approximate." Military grid. AMS 1.
